title: #209 Tennis, Anyone? (@MichaelKosta)
itunes:title: Tennis, Anyone? with Michael Kosta
description: Michael Kosta came over to my Los Angeles boarding house to have a nice talk with me about tennis. Kosta played since he was little and was even a professional for a few years before turning to standup. It was a fun conversation with two comics about a sport. And of course, there's some talk about anal, too.
